source.name: Nursery Growers and Greenhouse
source.description: A listing of all certified nursery growers and greenhouses which are licensed by the Department of Agriculture and Markets. Licensing of nursery growers and greenhouses is intended to prevent the introduction of injurious insects, noxious weeds, and plant diseases into the state.
